# Prometheus Alerts

This directory contains Prometheus alerting rules, recording rules, and configuration files for monitoring AWS resources.

## Contents

This directory will contain:
- Metrics collection and storage configurations
- Alerting rules for AWS resources
- Grafana dashboard templates
- Custom exporters for AWS services
- Recording rules for complex queries

